main

Class Params

  • java.lang.Object
    • main.Params

  • public class Params
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is to store all the parameters for the robot. Only store things here that will not change. i.e descriptions about our hardware, regular constants like speed etc. Put units beside each value. Constants stored include: SERVER_IP, TRACK, WHEEL_RAD, SENSOR_DIST, SPEED, TURN_SPEED, ACCEL, SEARCH_THRESHOLD, TILE_LENGTH, DIFF_THRESHOLD, TEAM_ID
